comments.comment: I always cringe when people show me their phone-recorded videos of concerts they went to. "Maybe it helps you relive the moment, but all I experience is a shitty miniature video with absolutely crap sound coming from your tinny iPhone speaker" hahaha; Are the days of fan photos gone (a shame)? Nearly got kicked out of a gig once for taking a photo on my phone.
